data.description: Looking for a home on the west side of town with a large lot and located on a quiet cul-de-sac street? Well look no further than this 4 bedroom 3 bath split level home! Sitting on  almost a 1/2 acre, this home features hardwood floors, open floor plan, modern updated finishes throughout, good size bedrooms, 2 pantries, and a large master suite accompanied by an updated shower. Outside enjoy your evenings grilling on the beautiful back deck or entertaining in the large yard. Make sure to contact David Renberg to see this home today, 785-236-9438!!
